      "full_text": "\ud83d\udea8 MASSIVE STATEMENT BY SAHIBZADA FARHAN ON THE HUNDRED LEAGUE \ud83d\udea8 \n\nSahibzada Farhan said \ud83d\udde3\ufe0f \n\n\"It's not in our hand who picks us and who doesn't. Wherever we get an opportunity and whoever is interested can pick us. We are ready to play that league, and where people aren't interested is [not something we focus on ] .\"",
