      "conversation_id_str": "2025993280195117183",
      "community_id_str": null,
      "community_name": null,
      "text": null,
      "full_text": "The picture is becoming clear now\u2026 the path for the Indian team hasn't been easy. A single day\u2019s slip-up now seems to be weighing heavily on our dreams. It has come to a point where winning our own matches isn't enough; we also have to pray for a South African victory. Both upcoming matches must be won at any cost.\nBut this is the same team for whom 142 crore hearts beat. When the love and blessings of the nation are with them, even miracles turn into history.",
      "source": "",
